WEBVTT

00:01.532 --> 00:04.605
OKAY, LISTEN UP, EVERYBODY!
GATHER ROUND.

00:04.605 --> 00:09.680
I WANT TO THANK YOU ALL FOR A
GREAT FIRST DAY BACK AT WORK

00:09.680 --> 00:11.242
AFTER THE SHUTDOWN.

00:11.242 --> 00:12.613
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:14.145 --> 00:16.047
TO SHOW THAT THEY APPRECIATE

00:16.047 --> 00:18.449
EVERYONE STICKING WITH
THE COMPANY,

00:18.449 --> 00:21.122
THE POWERS BROTHERS ARE GIVING
EVERY EMPLOYEE

00:21.122 --> 00:23.023
A THANKSGIVING TURKEY.

00:23.023 --> 00:24.525
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

00:24.525 --> 00:27.328
GOT ´EM RIGHT HERE, GEORGE.

00:27.328 --> 00:28.459
HERE YOU GO.

00:33.104 --> 00:34.535
WHAT THE HELL?

00:34.535 --> 00:37.308
THE OVEN´S GONNA BE LIKE, "HEY,
IS IT IN YET?"

00:44.675 --> 00:46.517
HEY, GEORGE.
LONG TIME, NO SEE.

00:46.517 --> 00:50.751
WELL, IF IT ISN´T MY LYING,
SCAMMING HALF BROTHER GEORGE.

00:50.751 --> 00:53.684
CAN I TALK TO YOU IN YOUR
OFFICE?

00:53.684 --> 00:57.088
OH, HEY, DUDE, HOW WAS YOUR
TRIP OVER HERE?

00:57.088 --> 01:00.631
DID YOU SKITCH ON THE BUMPER
OF A BUS?

01:00.631 --> 01:03.194
DID YOU CATCH SOME MAD AIR?

01:03.194 --> 01:05.096
DID YOU GET ALL SAD

01:05.096 --> 01:09.600
WHEN YOU SAW PEOPLE YOUR AGE
DRIVING BY IN CARS?

01:09.600 --> 01:11.402
NO. DO YOU GET ALL SAD

01:11.402 --> 01:15.276
WHEN YOU SEE PEOPLE YOUR AGE
BEING DRIVEN BY IN HEARSES?

01:17.308 --> 01:19.350
HEY, THAT´S MY MOM, OKAY?

01:19.350 --> 01:22.082
SHE´S NOT GONNA
BE IN A HEARSE.

01:22.082 --> 01:24.415
I´M GONNA HAVE
HER HEAD FROZEN,

01:24.415 --> 01:27.488
THEN I´M GONNA PUT IT IN THE
REFRIGERATOR.

01:27.488 --> 01:31.422
SO THAT WAY WHEN I GET ICE
CREAM, IT´LL BE A DOUBLE TREAT.

01:31.422 --> 01:34.094
GEORGE, I GOT SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU.

01:34.094 --> 01:36.197
LOOK, MAN, I KNOW YOU´RE
HERE FOR MONEY,

01:36.197 --> 01:38.129
BUT YOU´RE NOT GETTING MORE
THAN 10 BUCKS.

01:38.129 --> 01:39.570
I DON´T NEED ANY MONEY.

01:39.570 --> 01:41.832
I CAME HERE TO TELL YOU THAT OUR
DAD´S REALLY SICK.

01:41.832 --> 01:43.604
ALL RIGHT, $20.

01:43.604 --> 01:47.578
NOW, HOP ON YOUR BOARD AND GO
CRACK YOUR HUEVOS ON A HANDRAIL.

01:49.610 --> 01:51.782
I´M SERIOUS, DUDE.
HE´S GOT KIDNEY DISEASE.

01:51.782 --> 01:53.544
I JUST TALKED
TO HIM LAST WEEK.

01:53.544 --> 01:55.616
IF HE WAS SICK, WHY DIDN´T HE
SAY ANYTHING?

01:55.616 --> 01:58.118
HE´S FIGURED HE´S PUT YOU
THROUGH ENOUGH ALREADY.

01:58.118 --> 01:59.720
HE DOESN´T WANT
TO WORRY YOU.

01:59.720 --> 02:02.753
HE NEEDS A NEW KIDNEY, MAN.
I´M GONNA GIVE HIM ONE OF MINE.

02:02.753 --> 02:05.456
MAN, THAT´S HARD-CORE.

02:05.456 --> 02:07.127
I CAME OVER ´CAUSE I THOUGHT

02:07.127 --> 02:09.200
MAYBE I COULD GET MOM AND DAD
IN FROM PHOENIX

02:09.200 --> 02:12.303
AND THE WHOLE FAMILY COULD BE
TOGETHER FOR THANKSGIVING.

02:12.303 --> 02:14.605
YEAH. HAVE TO DEAL
WITH MY MOM,

02:14.605 --> 02:17.208
BUT, YEAH, MAYBE WE COULD DO IT
AT MY HOUSE.

02:17.208 --> 02:19.870
OH, DUDE, THAT´D BE GREAT.
THAT´D REALLY CHEER DAD UP.

02:22.213 --> 02:23.544
I´LL CALL HIM.

02:28.249 --> 02:31.322
SEE YOU AT THANKSGIVING.

02:31.322 --> 02:32.853
HEY, HERE!

02:32.853 --> 02:36.227
STUFF THIS WITH A CROUTON
AND STAY HOME!

02:36.227 --> 02:38.889
GEORGE!

02:38.889 --> 02:41.362
GEORGE, WHAT THE HELL WAS HE
TALKING ABOUT --

02:41.362 --> 02:43.163
"SEE YOU AT THANKSGIVING?"

02:43.163 --> 02:45.766
LOOK, MOM, I DECIDED TO INVITE
MANNY AND HIS FAMILY OVER.

02:45.766 --> 02:47.338
NO. HELL, NO.

02:47.338 --> 02:48.839
YOU KNOW, IT´S BAD ENOUGH

02:48.839 --> 02:50.901
YOU LET THAT IDIOT BACK
INTO YOUR LIFE.

02:50.901 --> 02:53.504
WHY DO YOU HAVE TO SHOVE HIM
INTO MINE?

02:53.504 --> 02:56.377
MANNY´S SICK, MOM.
HE´S GOT KIDNEY DISEASE.

02:56.377 --> 02:58.579
WELL, WHY DIDN´T YOU SAY SO?

02:58.579 --> 03:00.781
OF COURSE MANNY CAN COME.

03:00.781 --> 03:03.914
THIS YEAR WHEN WE GO
AROUND THE TABLE

03:03.914 --> 03:07.318
AND SAY WHAT
WE´RE THANKFUL FOR,

03:07.318 --> 03:08.889
LET ME GO FIRST.

03:12.723 --> 03:15.526
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

03:25.806 --> 03:29.480
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

03:31.482 --> 03:36.887
♫ THE LOW RIDER
IS A LITTLE HIGHER ♫

04:03.774 --> 04:07.618
THAT TURKEY LOOKS LIKE A
PTERODACTYL.

04:07.618 --> 04:11.422
AND HOW DO YOU SPELL
"PTERODACTYL"?

04:14.585 --> 04:17.628
THAT TURKEY
LOOKS LIKE A DUCK.

04:17.628 --> 04:21.292
HEY, MOM, LOOK AT THIS ANTIQUE
CHARM BRACELET

04:21.292 --> 04:22.863
GRANDMA LYDIA GAVE ME.

04:22.863 --> 04:24.635
SHE GOT IT IN ITALY.

04:29.570 --> 04:33.003
LYDIA, YOU SHOULDN´T
SPOIL THE KIDS.

04:33.003 --> 04:36.647
WHY NOT?
SHE SPOILED MY MARRIAGE.

04:36.647 --> 04:38.609
SHE SPOILED HER SON.

04:38.609 --> 04:39.850
OH, LOOK.

04:39.850 --> 04:41.612
THE GUACAMOLE´S TURNING BROWN

04:41.612 --> 04:43.654
JUST ´CAUSE SHE´S SITTING
NEXT TO IT.

04:43.654 --> 04:47.988
ANGIE, I JUST CAN´T HELP
SPOILING THESE CHILDREN.

04:47.988 --> 04:49.990
THEY ARE SO ADORABLE.

04:49.990 --> 04:53.664
AND BESIDES, HAVING A FEMALE
GRANDMOTHER

04:53.664 --> 04:55.666
WILL BE GOOD FOR THEM.

04:57.468 --> 05:02.002
LUCKY FOR YOU,
DRAG QUEENS COUNT.

05:02.002 --> 05:03.574
GREAT GAME.

05:03.574 --> 05:06.907
YEAH.
IT´S PRETTY CLOSE.

05:06.907 --> 05:08.709
VERY CLOSE.

05:08.709 --> 05:11.882
YOU KNOW, IF I´D KNOWN YOU WERE
SICK, MAN, I WOULD HAVE CALLED.

05:11.882 --> 05:13.444
I DIDN´T TELL YOU

05:13.444 --> 05:15.516
BECAUSE I DIDN´T WANT YOU TO
FEEL SORRY FOR ME.

05:15.516 --> 05:18.449
YOU KNOW, I´M WORRIED
ABOUT MY DAD.

05:21.522 --> 05:24.395
HE´S GOT THAT SLEEP APNEA
SNORING THING

05:24.395 --> 05:27.057
WHERE YOUR HEART STOPS.

05:27.057 --> 05:28.929
HE LIKES TO SLEEP ON THE COUCH,

05:28.929 --> 05:31.732
AND SOMETIMES I HAVE
A LADY OVER.

05:31.732 --> 05:34.334
TOUGH TO GET A KISS
FROM YOUR DATE

05:34.334 --> 05:38.539
AFTER SHE´S JUST SEEN YOU GIVE
YOUR DAD MOUTH-TO-MOUTH.

05:41.572 --> 05:44.745
YOU KNOW, I THOUGHT ABOUT
CALLING.

05:44.745 --> 05:47.448
FORGET ABOUT IT.
IT´S OKAY.

05:47.448 --> 05:49.380
YEAH.

05:49.380 --> 05:51.351
OH, GREAT!

05:51.351 --> 05:53.123
TOUCHDOWN!

05:53.123 --> 05:55.526
ALL RIGHT!
[ LAUGHS ]

06:01.462 --> 06:03.994
I THOUGHT YOU WERE FOR UCLA.

06:11.942 --> 06:13.504
ANGE, ARE WE READY TO EAT?

06:13.504 --> 06:15.506
YEAH, WE´RE JUST WAITING FOR
YOUR BROTHER.

06:15.506 --> 06:18.549
WOW, SOMETHING SURE
SMELLS GREAT.

06:18.549 --> 06:20.581
WHY, THANK YOU, GEORGE.

06:20.581 --> 06:24.114
I HAD IT BLENDED IN A
PERFUMERY IN PARIS.

06:24.114 --> 06:26.957
THEY REALLY CAPTURED THE SMELL
OF BAKED TURKEY.

06:28.659 --> 06:30.691
CARMEN, GET OFF THE PHONE!

06:30.691 --> 06:33.594
ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY,
GRAB A DISH.

06:33.594 --> 06:35.996
OH, ANGIE, THIS IS SO GREAT --

06:35.996 --> 06:39.930
TWO FAMILIES COMING
TOGETHER FOR THANKSGIVING.

06:39.930 --> 06:46.136
WHAT IS THE NAME OF GEORGE´S
STRANGE FRIEND AGAIN?

06:46.136 --> 06:47.407
ERNIE.

06:47.407 --> 06:49.409
AH, YES, ERNIE.

06:49.409 --> 06:53.183
I WILL NOT SIT NEXT TO HIM.

06:53.183 --> 06:55.185
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

06:55.185 --> 06:57.618
GEORGE.

06:57.618 --> 06:59.920
GEORGE, SO GLAD YOU
COULD MAKE IT.

07:02.092 --> 07:03.654
THIS IS FOR YOU.

07:03.654 --> 07:07.097
SORRY. I KIND OF DRANK
HALF OF IF.

07:08.699 --> 07:11.802
WELL, WHY DON´T WE JUST CALL
THIS YOUR BOTTLE?

07:14.465 --> 07:16.467
YOU´RE NOT SUPPOSED TO DRINK.

07:16.467 --> 07:18.569
YOU´RE GIVING YOUR FATHER
A KIDNEY.

07:18.569 --> 07:20.110
I CAN´T GIVE HIM MY KIDNEY.

07:20.110 --> 07:22.943
THE FINAL TESTS CAME IN, AND
WE´RE NOT COMPATIBLE.

07:25.476 --> 07:27.778
ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY,
LET´S EAT!

07:29.950 --> 07:31.982
WHAT´S HAPPENING, LITTLE
BROTHER?

07:31.982 --> 07:35.986
HEY, MAX, WE FINALLY MADE IT TO
THE BIG TABLE, HUH?

07:42.563 --> 07:45.936
BUT I STILL GOT THE SAME CHAIR!

07:49.139 --> 07:52.102
THIS IS A VERY SPECIAL
THANKSGIVING.

07:52.102 --> 07:56.476
I MEAN, WHO WOULD HAVE THOUGHT A
GUY WHO GREW UP AN ONLY CHILD

07:56.476 --> 08:00.480
WOULD BE STANDING IN FRONT OF A
FATHER AND A BROTHER

08:00.480 --> 08:03.854
AND A MOTHER
WHO LIED ABOUT ALL OF YOU?

08:05.516 --> 08:10.761
TO THE FIRST OF MANY HOLIDAYS
WE´RE GONNA SPEND TOGETHER,

08:10.761 --> 08:12.563
AND TO MY BROTHER,

08:12.563 --> 08:18.629
WHO´S SHOWN ME WHAT REAL COURAGE
IS BY GIVING MANNY A KIDNEY.

08:18.629 --> 08:22.533
AND IT´S BECAUSE OF THIS HERO --

08:22.533 --> 08:24.174
I´M SORRY --

08:24.174 --> 08:28.709
THAT I´M GONNA HAVE THE TIME TO
GET TO KNOW MY FATHER.

08:28.709 --> 08:30.611
NO, YOU´RE NOT.

08:30.611 --> 08:33.644
JORGITO´S KIDNEY DIDN´T MATCH.

08:36.186 --> 08:37.788
BUT THE DOCTOR SAID...

08:38.889 --> 08:40.591
I KNOW.

08:40.591 --> 08:46.657
I´M AB NEGATIVE, BUT OUR BLOOD´S
NOT A COMPLETE MATCH.

08:46.657 --> 08:48.599
I´M SORRY, DAD.

08:48.599 --> 08:51.802
IT´S NOT YOUR FAULT.

08:55.205 --> 08:59.109
I´M FEELING A LITTLE
RESPONSIBLE HERE, MANNY.

08:59.109 --> 09:02.843
I PRAYED FOR YOUR DEATH FOR
A LONG TIME.

09:04.615 --> 09:07.217
BENNY, YOUR PRAYERS DIDN´T
CAUSE THIS.

09:07.217 --> 09:13.754
OKAY...BUT I SPECIFICALLY ASKED
FOR KIDNEY DISEASE.

09:17.828 --> 09:20.130
THERE´S STILL ONE LAST HOPE.

09:20.130 --> 09:22.733
YOU DO HAVE ANOTHER SON.

09:27.738 --> 09:29.700
GEORGE IS AB NEGATIVE.

09:29.700 --> 09:31.842
REMEMBER? YOU REMEMBER.

09:35.575 --> 09:38.308
AT THE BLOOD DRIVE, THE NURSE
WANTED YOU TO GIVE MORE BLOOD

09:38.308 --> 09:40.150
BECAUSE YOU WERE SO RARE.

09:40.150 --> 09:43.213
AAH!

09:45.786 --> 09:47.117
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

09:47.117 --> 09:49.720
WELL, I DON´T KNOW
ABOUT A KIDNEY,

09:49.720 --> 09:51.792
BUT WHO WANTS A DRUMSTICK?

10:07.137 --> 10:08.839
WANT SOME DESSERT?

10:08.839 --> 10:10.811
I´M GONNA DIE.

10:13.744 --> 10:15.886
MY LAST THANKSGIVING.

10:15.886 --> 10:18.118
MY LAST FOOTBALL GAME.

10:18.118 --> 10:20.120
MY LAST EVERYTHING.

10:20.120 --> 10:24.895
PIE´S PRETTY GOOD.

10:24.895 --> 10:27.728
GEORGE, I´M SCARED.

10:27.728 --> 10:30.330
MANNY, I KNOW WHAT YOU
MUST BE THINKING.

10:30.330 --> 10:31.902
WHAT´S THAT?

10:31.902 --> 10:34.134
THAT WE´RE STILL STRANGERS TO
EACH OTHER, MAN,

10:34.134 --> 10:37.007
AND IT´S NOT RIGHT FOR YOU TO
ASK ME FOR MY KIDNEY.

10:37.007 --> 10:40.370
NO, THAT´S NOT WHAT I´M
THINKING.

10:40.370 --> 10:42.342
COME ON, MAN, DON´T DO THIS.

10:42.342 --> 10:45.415
I´VE ONLY SEEN YOU THREE
TIMES IN MY LIFE,

10:45.415 --> 10:49.179
AND ONE OF THOSE TIMES, I
PUNCHED YOU.

10:49.179 --> 10:51.021
I NEED A KIDNEY.

10:53.854 --> 10:56.226
YOU CAN GIVE ME THE
GIFT OF LIFE.

10:56.226 --> 11:03.063
YOU KNOW, ANGIE´S KIND OF IN
CHARGE OF THE GIFT GIVING.

11:03.063 --> 11:05.195
I KNOW I´M ASKING A HUGE
SACRIFICE,

11:05.195 --> 11:07.197
AND I PROBABLY
DON´T DESERVE IT.

11:07.197 --> 11:09.770
I´M WITH YOU SO FAR.

11:09.770 --> 11:11.271
IT´S YOUR DECISION.

11:11.271 --> 11:13.373
I RESPECT WHATEVER YOU DO.

11:18.949 --> 11:20.050
GEORGE...

11:20.050 --> 11:21.782
OH.

11:21.782 --> 11:24.054
CAN I TALK TO YOU?

11:24.054 --> 11:25.816
SURE, LYDIA.

11:25.816 --> 11:28.688
YOUR FATHER NEEDS YOUR HELP.

11:28.688 --> 11:32.993
HE´S AT THE BOTTOM OF THE
TRANSPLANT LIST.

11:32.993 --> 11:34.694
JORGE...

11:34.694 --> 11:36.326
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

11:41.872 --> 11:43.874
COME ON, LYDIA, PLEASE.

11:43.874 --> 11:47.477
I SHOULDN´T BEG.

11:47.477 --> 11:54.184
IF YOU DON´T GIVE YOUR KIDNEY TO
THE MAN WHO GAVE YOU LIFE,

11:54.184 --> 11:58.218
I WILL COME WHERE YOU´RE
SLEEPING,

11:58.218 --> 12:01.491
AND I WILL RIP IT OUT MYSELF.

12:07.227 --> 12:09.399
I KIND OF MISS THE BEGGING.

12:12.232 --> 12:14.734
CAN YOU BELIEVE THE NERVE OF
THAT GUY,

12:14.734 --> 12:18.338
ASKING YOU TO SAVE HIS LIFE
AFTER HE WALKED OUT OF YOURS?

12:18.338 --> 12:22.112
LOOK, IF I WERE IN HIS PLACE,
MOM, I´D DO THE SAME THING.

12:22.112 --> 12:23.974
HE HAS NO OTHER OPTIONS.

12:23.974 --> 12:25.976
WELL, THERE´S ONE I LIKE.

12:25.976 --> 12:27.848
IT SOUNDS LIKE THIS.

12:27.848 --> 12:30.951
[ IMITATING MONITOR BEEPING ]

12:30.951 --> 12:34.324
[ IMITATING FLATLINE ]

12:34.324 --> 12:35.485
MOM!

12:40.530 --> 12:44.264
SO...WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO, HONEY?

12:44.264 --> 12:45.996
I DON´T KNOW, ANGIE.

12:45.996 --> 12:47.898
I MEAN, HE IS MY DAD.

12:47.898 --> 12:50.100
NO, HE´S NOT.

12:50.100 --> 12:51.902
I WAS YOUR DAD.

12:51.902 --> 12:53.874
I BROUGHT HOME THE BACON,

12:53.874 --> 12:57.507
I GAVE YOU YOUR FIRST BEER, I
TAUGHT YOU HOW TO SHAVE.

12:58.879 --> 13:01.011
YEAH, ALL IN THE SAME DAY.

13:01.011 --> 13:04.154
GEORGE, IF YOU
HADN´T BEEN DRUNK,

13:04.154 --> 13:06.556
THOSE CUTS WOULD HAVE HURT.

13:08.018 --> 13:10.160
ANGIE, WHAT DO YOU THINK
I SHOULD DO?

13:10.160 --> 13:13.163
THIS IS
YOUR DECISION, HONEY.

13:13.163 --> 13:15.365
I CAN´T MAKE IT FOR YOU.

13:15.365 --> 13:17.567
YOU KNOW ALL THE RISKS.

13:17.567 --> 13:22.132
BUT NO MATTER WHAT YOU DECIDE,
I´LL STAND BY YOU.

13:22.132 --> 13:25.275
I CAN´T BELIEVE YOU ARE EVEN
THINKING ABOUT THIS.

13:25.275 --> 13:26.907
YOU´RE HIS SON.

13:26.907 --> 13:30.410
WHAT IF YOU END UP WITH BAD
KIDNEYS LIKE HIM?

13:30.410 --> 13:33.914
ARE YOU GONNA TAKE THE CHANCE
OF JUST HAVING ONE?

13:33.914 --> 13:35.315
HEY, I GOT FOUR SPARE KIDNEYS

13:35.315 --> 13:37.447
SLEEPING UP IN THEIR
ROOM RIGHT NOW.

13:42.522 --> 13:44.354
GEORGE.

13:44.354 --> 13:47.457
WHAT´S THE USE OF HAVING KIDS
IF YOU CAN´T USE THEM FOR PARTS?

13:48.458 --> 13:50.230
OKAY. EXACTLY.

13:50.230 --> 13:52.032
NOW, WHAT IF I NEED A KIDNEY,

13:52.032 --> 13:54.204
BUT YOU´VE ALREADY GIVEN YOUR
SPARE TO MANNY?

13:54.204 --> 13:55.966
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?

13:55.966 --> 13:58.238
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHAT YOU´RE
SUPPOSED TO DO?

13:58.238 --> 13:59.970
PLEASE TELL ME.

13:59.970 --> 14:02.212
[ IMITATING FLATLINE ]

14:08.879 --> 14:10.850
WHAT ARE YOU TWO DOING UP?

14:10.850 --> 14:12.883
HE COULDN´T SLEEP, AND
HE WOKE ME UP.

14:12.883 --> 14:14.985
YOU KNOW WHAT I DO WHEN
I CAN´T SLEEP?

14:14.985 --> 14:17.227
I JUST READ SOME OF
CARMEN´S POETRY.

14:18.989 --> 14:23.033
"IF MY TEARS COULD WATER THE
WORLD, I..."

14:28.999 --> 14:33.873
AFTER THE OPERATION, I´M GONNA
HIDE YOUR PAIN MEDICATION.

14:37.277 --> 14:38.909
WHY CAN´T YOU SLEEP?

14:38.909 --> 14:40.951
I DON´T WANT DAD TO DIE.

14:40.951 --> 14:44.985
I DON´T WANT YOU TO HAVE THE
KIDNEY OPERATION.

14:44.985 --> 14:48.058
MAX, YOU SHOULDN´T EVEN BE
THINKING ABOUT THIS.

14:48.058 --> 14:50.160
WHAT IF THE OPERATION GOES BAD?

14:50.160 --> 14:53.463
LOOK, MAX, I´M GONNA BE
AROUND A LONG TIME, OKAY?

14:53.463 --> 14:57.027
LONG ENOUGH TO BE A STRAIN
ON YOUR MARRIAGE.

15:00.931 --> 15:02.472
I´LL LIVE IN YOUR GARAGE.

15:02.472 --> 15:06.576
MAYBE I´LL LOSE IT AND START
CALLING YOUR WIFE "MOMMY."

15:06.576 --> 15:08.979
BUT I WILL STILL
BE HERE, OKAY?

15:08.979 --> 15:12.142
DAD, I DON´T WANT YOU TO
DO THIS.

15:12.142 --> 15:14.314
PLEASE, DON´T DO THIS.

15:16.086 --> 15:18.048
OKAY, I THINK HE HEARD
YOU, HONEY.

15:18.048 --> 15:21.151
COME ON.
LET´S GO UPSTAIRS AND GO TO BED.

15:25.956 --> 15:28.098
[ IMITATING FLATLINE ]

15:39.609 --> 15:41.471
WHERE´S GEORGE?

15:41.471 --> 15:43.673
HE´S OUT ON A WALK, THINKING.

15:43.673 --> 15:45.475
THAT´S GOOD.

15:45.475 --> 15:47.277
I´M GLAD YOU´RE BOTH HERE.

15:47.277 --> 15:50.680
I HAVE SOMETHING I HAVE
TO TELL YOU.

15:50.680 --> 15:54.484
I HAD A DREAM LAST NIGHT.

15:54.484 --> 15:56.956
GOD CAME TO ME.

15:56.956 --> 16:01.691
HE SAID HE DOESN´T WANT YOU TO
TAKE MY SON´S KIDNEY.

16:01.691 --> 16:03.533
HE WANTS YOU TO DIE.

16:11.601 --> 16:14.074
OKAY, I THINK I MADE MY
DECISION.

16:14.074 --> 16:16.176
OKAY, YOU HEARD IT.
IT´S A "NO."

16:16.176 --> 16:17.247
IT´S OVER. THAT´S IT.

16:17.247 --> 16:20.150
MOM, MOM, LET ME DO THIS.

16:20.150 --> 16:23.453
I´M GONNA GIVE YOU MY KIDNEY.

16:23.453 --> 16:25.455
THANK GOD!

16:25.455 --> 16:27.257
WHAT?

16:27.257 --> 16:32.192
I DON´T KNOW WHERE MY KIDNEY IS,
BUT I THINK YOU´RE DAMAGING IT.

16:33.623 --> 16:36.396
JUST TELL ME WHAT I NEED TO DO
WITH THE TESTS AND EVERYTHING.

16:36.396 --> 16:41.331
I´LL MAKE ALL THE ARRANGEMENTS,
AND GOD BLESS YOU, GEORGE.

16:46.336 --> 16:48.338
MAYBE WE SHOULD GO.

16:51.241 --> 16:54.414
GEORGE...THANK YOU.

16:58.448 --> 17:00.420
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

17:00.420 --> 17:03.623
IF SOMETHING HAPPENS TO YOU,
WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO?

17:03.623 --> 17:06.496
WHAT HAPPENED TO "I´LL STAND BY
YOU NO MATTER WHAT"?

17:06.496 --> 17:11.201
I NEVER THOUGHT YOU´D AGREE TO
HAVE YOUR KIDNEY CUT OUT.

17:11.201 --> 17:15.065
YOU CAN´T EVEN HANDLE A COLD,
YOU BIG BABY.

17:15.065 --> 17:18.068
WELL, I THINK I´M DOING THE
RIGHT THING.

17:18.068 --> 17:19.639
I´M BEING NOBLE, ANGIE.

17:19.639 --> 17:24.114
I DIDN´T MARRY A NOBLE MAN.
I MARRIED YOU.

17:24.114 --> 17:27.046
FOR ONCE, SHE´S RIGHT.
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU THINKING?

17:27.046 --> 17:31.381
LOOK, I´M THINKING THIS IS MY
CHANCE TO GIVE SOMETHING BACK.

17:31.381 --> 17:36.326
GROWING UP, IT WAS ALWAYS ABOUT
WHAT WE COULD TAKE FROM PEOPLE.

17:36.326 --> 17:38.258
WE KEPT NEIGHBORS´ PACKAGES.

17:40.790 --> 17:44.264
WE DID OUR CLOTHES SHOPPING
AT THE LAUNDROMAT.

17:46.196 --> 17:49.269
MOM, WE´RE THE REASON LUGGAGE
ISN´T ALLOWED

17:49.269 --> 17:51.701
AT THE ALL-YOU-CAN-EAT
RESTAURANTS.

17:53.273 --> 17:57.647
OUR WHOLE LIVES, WE NEVER
GAVE ANYTHING.

17:57.647 --> 17:59.679
WE´RE TAKERS, MOM.

17:59.679 --> 18:02.712
GEORGE, OF COURSE
WE´RE TAKERS.

18:02.712 --> 18:05.815
WE DON´T HAVE ANYTHING
TO GIVE.

18:08.188 --> 18:09.859
NOW I DO.

18:17.567 --> 18:18.828
THAT´S MY BEER.

18:18.828 --> 18:21.131
I CAN´T HELP IT!
I´M A TAKER!

18:24.574 --> 18:26.636
WHAT´S EVERYBODY YELLING ABOUT?

18:26.636 --> 18:29.809
YOU EXPLAIN THIS.

18:31.241 --> 18:33.183
WHAT´S GOING ON?

18:33.183 --> 18:37.287
MAX...

18:37.287 --> 18:39.189
I´M GONNA GIVE YOUR
GRANDPA A KIDNEY.

18:39.189 --> 18:40.450
NO!

18:40.450 --> 18:42.292
LISTEN TO ME, MAX.

18:42.292 --> 18:44.294
I´M SAVING A MAN´S LIFE.

18:44.294 --> 18:47.897
DAD, HE´S A STRANGER.

18:47.897 --> 18:50.600
HE´S SUPEROLD.

18:50.600 --> 18:54.864
DID YOU SEE THE HOCKEY STICK HE
GOT ME FOR MY BIRTHDAY?

18:54.864 --> 18:56.536
IT´S PLASTIC.

18:56.536 --> 18:59.509
ALL GOOD REASONS
TO LET HIM DIE.

18:59.509 --> 19:02.442
BUT LOOK AT
IT THIS WAY, SON --

19:02.442 --> 19:07.217
WHAT IF I WAS SICK AND THERE WAS
A WAY YOU COULD HELP ME?

19:07.217 --> 19:09.549
WOULDN´T YOU DO IT?

19:12.222 --> 19:13.653
YEAH.

19:13.653 --> 19:17.487
WELL, THAT´S WHAT I´M DOING
FOR MY DAD.

19:19.889 --> 19:22.462
COME ON, MAN, THEY DO THESE
SURGERIES ALL THE TIME.

19:22.462 --> 19:23.893
I´M GONNA BE FINE, MAX.

19:23.893 --> 19:25.195
ARE YOU SURE?

19:25.195 --> 19:26.536
ABSOLUTELY.

19:26.536 --> 19:29.899
YOU CAN TELL EVERYONE THAT
YOUR DAD´S A HERO.

19:29.899 --> 19:34.374
I´LL COME DOWN TO YOUR SCHOOL
AND SHOW OFF MY SCAR.

19:34.374 --> 19:36.806
THERE´S GONNA BE A SCAR?

19:36.806 --> 19:38.648
BUT YOU´RE A BIG BABY.

19:38.648 --> 19:41.681
YOU CAN´T EVEN HANDLE A COLD.

19:43.553 --> 19:50.189
[ Weakly ] "MAX, CAN YOU PUT
SOME HONEY IN MY TEA?

19:50.189 --> 19:54.524
IT HURTS EVERY
TIME I SWALLOW."

19:54.524 --> 19:58.368
IT WAS A VERY BAD COLD!

19:58.368 --> 20:00.530
THE KIND PEOPLE USED
TO DIE FROM!

20:01.731 --> 20:05.875
I CAN NEVER DO NOTHING
IN THIS HOUSE!

20:09.879 --> 20:11.481
[ SNORING ]

20:13.283 --> 20:14.544
[ SNORTS ]

20:16.816 --> 20:19.789
GEORGE, SHE
STOPPED BREATHING.

20:19.789 --> 20:24.223
MAYBE IT´S SLEEP APNEA,
AND HER HEART STOPPED.

20:24.223 --> 20:27.827
IT´S GOD´S WILL.

20:27.827 --> 20:31.961
I THINK SHE NEEDS
MOUTH-TO-MOUTH.

20:31.961 --> 20:34.564
SHE LIVED A GOOD LIFE.

20:34.564 --> 20:38.408
GEORGE, IN A FEW MINUTES, HER
BRAIN WILL BE DEAD!

20:38.408 --> 20:41.711
ALL RIGHT,
I´LL RESUSCITATE HER.
